Healthylabs.ai — End-to-End Medical 
Knowledge Pipeline  
1. Core Design Philosophy 
Healthylabs.ai is designed as a medical-grade knowledge refinery, not a generic RAG system. 
Key principles: 
• Not all data is equal → Trust tiering is mandatory 
• Embeddings are irreversible → All safety checks happen before vectorization 
• Medicine contains contradictions → The system must detect them 
• Every answer must be traceable → Auditability is non-negotiable 
