3. Advanced Medical Cleaning & Safety Layer 
This layer ensures no unsafe data ever reaches the vector database. 
3.1 PII / PHI Scrubbing (Hard Gate) 
• Specialized medical NER models detect: 
o Patient names 
o IDs 
o Addresses 
o Dates of birth 
• Detection confidence is explicitly measured 
Quarantine Rule: 
• If PHI confidence < 95% 
o Document is diverted to a Quarantine Index 
o Never embedded 
o Requires human review 
This prevents silent PHI leakage — a critical medical compliance requirement. 
3.2 Medical De-Noising 
• Boilerplate & legal disclaimers removed via hash-based pattern detection 
• Unicode normalization 
• PDF structural fixes: 
o Broken hyphenation (anti-\nbiotics → antibiotics) 
o Column bleed 
o OCR artifacts 
3.3 Retraction Awareness 
• All Tier 1 & Tier 2 documents are checked against retraction databases 
• Retracted documents are: 
o Marked deprecated 
o Excluded from citation 
o Preserved for audit history 
